==Related==
[[Angela Carter]]'s ''[[The Bloody Chamber]]'' (in the short story &quot;Puss in Boots&quot;) gives another representation of Pantalone. The interpretation uses the spelling 'Pantaloon', but he follows a very similar description and ends up dead.

